I don't understand Cantonese.

537
00:35:49,207 --> 00:35:50,959
I don't mean anything else.

538
00:35:50,959 --> 00:35:53,568
I'm not trying to take advantage of you.

539
00:35:53,568 --> 00:35:56,799
If you want to leave now, I can take you to the airport right away.

540
00:35:57,999 --> 00:36:00,502
Wait here. I'll get the car.

541
00:36:00,502 --> 00:36:02,342
Fang Shun Hua!

542
00:36:04,250 --> 00:36:05,842
Did you call me?

543
00:36:07,250 --> 00:36:10,209
Actually, I have some savings, too.

544
00:36:10,209 --> 00:36:13,799
We can work together to make the restaurant bigger.

545
00:36:31,494 --> 00:36:33,925
I still don't understand.

546
00:36:40,933 --> 00:36:42,967
I figured you'd be here.

547
00:37:27,999 --> 00:37:30,759
Mr. Bai, what are you doing here?

548
00:37:30,759 --> 00:37:33,248
Village Chief, what are you doing here?

549
00:37:33,248 --> 00:37:34,429
I...

550
00:37:34,429 --> 00:37:38,883
I borrowed some crab cages from a friend.

551
00:37:40,083 --> 00:37:42,753
You missed quite a show.

552
00:37:42,753 --> 00:37:43,794
What show?

553
00:37:43,794 --> 00:37:46,292
Your son fell into the water and almost drowned.

554
00:37:46,292 --> 00:37:48,792
My... Da Wu!

555
00:37:48,792 --> 00:37:50,967
- Da Wu!
- He almost didn't make it.

556
00:37:53,999 --> 00:37:55,925
Where is he now?

557
00:37:56,735 --> 00:37:58,786
When they were looking for you,

558
00:37:58,786 --> 00:38:00,799
did you want them to find you?

559
00:38:03,867 --> 00:38:05,000
Or maybe the person they were looking for

560
00:38:05,000 --> 00:38:06,083
wasn't really you,

561
00:38:06,083 --> 00:38:07,360
but someone who doesn't drink excessively

562
00:38:07,360 --> 00:38:08,660
and run away from problems.

563
00:38:08,660 --> 00:38:10,842
Someone who won't make them worry.

564
00:38:18,193 --> 00:38:20,401
Village Chief.

565
00:38:20,401 --> 00:38:23,292
You've always hoped your son would bring honor to your family,

566
00:38:23,292 --> 00:38:26,799
but have you ever thought about what he really wants?

567
00:38:30,167 --> 00:38:31,368
What does he want?

568
00:38:31,368 --> 00:38:33,842
Are you asking me? How do I know?

569
00:38:37,711 --> 00:38:39,360
Da Wu didn't drown today,

570
00:38:39,360 --> 00:38:43,318
which means fate is giving you another chance to start over.

571
00:38:43,318 --> 00:38:46,167
You don't have to keep trapping yourself in the past.

572
00:38:46,167 --> 00:38:50,050
It was you who chose to stay trapped there.

573
00:38:52,299 --> 00:38:56,426
Also, haven't you sun-dried yourself long enough?

574
00:39:09,050 --> 00:39:11,967
What your son wants is actually simple.

575
00:39:13,603 --> 00:39:18,294
He just wants his dad to support his dreams

576
00:39:18,294 --> 00:39:20,085
and allow him to stay here

577
00:39:20,085 --> 00:39:22,718
to take care of everyone he cares about.

578
00:39:26,285 --> 00:39:28,327
What are you still standing here for?

579
00:39:28,327 --> 00:39:31,586
Go back and fix your relationship with your son.

580
00:39:31,586 --> 00:39:33,799
At least you still have the chance.

581
00:39:50,662 --> 00:39:53,009
What right do I have to talk about others?

582
00:40:00,334 --> 00:40:02,342
Today wasn't bad.

583
00:40:06,867 --> 00:40:09,050
Get the rice out.

584
00:40:26,933 --> 00:40:28,799
Done with sun-drying?

585
00:40:38,226 --> 00:40:40,678
Look at you.

586
00:40:40,678 --> 00:40:43,799
Why did you have to make such a big deal out of it?

587
00:40:44,520 --> 00:40:48,235
Last night, I dreamed about Hong Si and Si Ting.

588
00:40:48,235 --> 00:40:50,786
They came back happily and told me

589
00:40:50,786 --> 00:40:52,509
that they missed everyone.

590
00:40:52,509 --> 00:40:54,601
They wanted to come back and see us.

591
00:40:54,601 --> 00:40:59,125
So, I thought maybe I could bring them back today.

592
00:40:59,125 --> 00:41:01,125
It has been so long.

593
00:41:01,125 --> 00:41:03,799
How could you still find them?

594
00:41:05,083 --> 00:41:08,601
I've always considered my son and daughter-in-law

595
00:41:08,601 --> 00:41:10,999
to be buried at sea.

596
00:41:10,999 --> 00:41:12,626
Even if you found them today,

597
00:41:12,626 --> 00:41:15,375
I would still send them back to the sea.

598
00:41:19,250 --> 00:41:23,250
Well, I'm very happy you came back safely.

599
00:41:23,250 --> 00:41:25,799
But why was it only me who came back?

600
00:41:29,042 --> 00:41:32,584
Ms. Shu Man, I really did my best.

601
00:41:32,584 --> 00:41:35,092
I couldn't hold onto them. I...

602
00:41:37,101 --> 00:41:38,417
I let them down.

603
00:41:38,417 --> 00:41:41,083
I let Si Ting down. I let them down.

604
00:41:41,083 --> 00:41:43,259
I really did my best.

605
00:41:44,518 --> 00:41:47,933
I'm so sorry...

606
00:41:47,933 --> 00:41:50,167
I'm so sorry for Hai Nuo.

607
00:41:50,167 --> 00:41:52,167
It was all because of me.

608
00:41:52,167 --> 00:41:54,643
If Hong Si and Si Ting were still here,

609
00:41:54,643 --> 00:41:56,933
they would definitely love her very much.

610
00:41:56,933 --> 00:41:58,643
I'm the one who hurt Hai Nuo.

611
00:41:58,643 --> 00:42:02,426
I made her lose her parents at such a young age.

612
00:42:15,485 --> 00:42:17,235
She still has me.

613
00:42:17,235 --> 00:42:19,867
And you all love Hai Nuo so much.

614
00:42:19,867 --> 00:42:21,842
There's also Da Wu.

615
00:42:22,626 --> 00:42:25,619
Although I also have some regrets,

616
00:42:25,619 --> 00:42:28,125
I've always told Hai Nuo

617
00:42:28,125 --> 00:42:31,009
that her parents are doing well.

618
00:42:31,009 --> 00:42:35,842
We should also live well so that they can be at peace.

619
00:42:36,487 --> 00:42:41,693
You drank so much as if our family is so unfortunate.

620
00:42:41,693 --> 00:42:44,925
Do you really wish for us to be unhappy?

621
00:42:47,167 --> 00:42:51,134
Fu Shou, you're also like my son.

622
00:42:51,134 --> 00:42:53,125
You keep tormenting yourself like this.

623
00:42:53,125 --> 00:42:56,634
Have you ever thought about how much it hurts me?

624
00:42:59,933 --> 00:43:03,478
I'm sorry.

625
00:43:03,478 --> 00:43:04,768
All right.

626
00:43:04,768 --> 00:43:06,417
Stop apologizing to me.

627
00:43:06,417 --> 00:43:07,594
You didn't do anything wrong.

628
00:43:07,594 --> 00:43:09,553
You didn't let anyone down.

629
00:43:09,553 --> 00:43:11,026
You should stop drinking.

630
00:43:11,026 --> 00:43:13,520
Take care of yourself and live well.

631
00:43:13,520 --> 00:43:16,799
Don't make us all worry anymore, okay?

632
00:43:17,786 --> 00:43:19,959
If you don't listen next time.

633
00:43:19,959 --> 00:43:23,967
I'll spank you with this.

634
00:43:47,900 --> 00:43:51,050
I promise you.

635
00:43:52,083 --> 00:43:54,603
Good.

636
00:43:54,603 --> 00:43:56,250
Luckily, we're still on time.

637
00:43:56,250 --> 00:43:57,344
Come on. Let's pray.

638
00:43:57,344 --> 00:44:00,353
Come on, everyone. Let's pray.

639
00:44:00,353 --> 00:44:02,160
Put the offerings here.

640
00:44:02,160 --> 00:44:04,718
Light four sticks of incense.
